&lt;h2&gt;Waiting List Co-ordinator&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Surgery Division is looking to appoint an Waiting List Co-ordinator on a permanent basis to Surgery &amp; Outpatients that will support patient pathways and directly support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need be experienced in the use of PAS and have an excellent understanding of the referral to treatment (RTT) pathway and Cancer pathway for Surgery patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will be managing the consultants inpatient waiting list and booking the patients pre-operative assessment with the surgical division, ensuring that patients are booked within target. This post is a 6 month fixed term position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be liaising with consultants/nurses, patients and management on various levels and ensuring that patients are booked in according to trust policy. You will also support the department andits processes by providing administration and clerical support and assisting with any clerical issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 10/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
